	<BR><SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">
In caprea
	</SPAN></SPAN></H3>

	<H4 CLASS="start center"><A NAME="346"></A>
346 Sauce for Wild Goat
	<BR><SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">
Ius in caprea
	</SPAN></H4>

	<P CLASS="justify">
Pepper, lovage, caraway, cumin, parsley, rue seed, honey, mustard, vinegar, broth and oil<SPAN CLASS="emend">.</SPAN>


